## `_work/` directory convention

All live agent state lives under `_work/`.

| Path | Purpose | Who writes it |
|---|---|---|
| `_work/stacks/` | Active stacks (registry + profiles) | Dev initial + `/spec` |
| `_work/build/<id>.yaml` | Per-story gate state | Orchestrator |
| `_work/build/test-registry.yaml` | Tests per story (G2.2) | Orchestrator |
| `_work/contracts/<id>/` | API/AST/DB/CLI snapshots (G2.3) | Orchestrator |
| `_work/visual-baseline/<id>/` | Visual baselines (G9.3) | Orchestrator |
| `_work/perf-baseline/<id>.json` | Perf baseline (G10) | Orchestrator |
| `_work/data-fixtures/<id>/` | Seed data (G13) | Orchestrator |
| `_work/ux/wireframes/` | HTML wireframes with `data-testid` | `/ux` |

